Ųin memory of our dear mother
Sarah McDonaugh (nee Nelson) 1940 2010
and our dear father
Thomas McDonaugh 1930 1996
This bench commemorates them both
and the happy summer days we spent together
at our favourite spot on the beach.
just a few feet from here.
Happy, timeless moments, never forgotten.
Leslie, Karen and Gaynor xxx"▐
